```
From our cross-team notes of RDSS: “Revisiting dissertation-to-Alma upcoming workflow using XSLT and ProQuest”
Also “Dissertation catalog loading from DataSpace/Proquest troubleshooting completed”
```

Yes, I agree this can be closed. I think we should consider whether having a "Dissertation" format would be helpful (instead of having them be "Books") as we develop the new workflow. But the items are in the catalog and discoverable now.
